name: Terra incognita - AI landscape works by Attila Simon

metadata.name: Terra incognita 1.
metadata.description:
Welcome to Terra incognita, a collection of artworks that investigates the intersection of photography and artificial intelligence. Through the use of advanced algorithms and machine learning techniques, this body of work delves into uncharted territories of aesthetics and perspective, offering a fresh take on the potential of technology in shaping the art world. Each piece in this collection is a unique, digital creation, presenting images that are entirely new and unseen before. Join me on this journey as we explore the boundless possibilities of AI in art and challenge traditional notions of artistic expression.
